        <p class="text-sm text-orange-300 font-semibold mb-3">5 points · S=1, H=4 · Interjection: "quiet!"</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">SH is SOWPODS-only and contains no vowels. It's one of the rare consonant-only plays in Scrabble — perfect for consonant-heavy racks in international games. TWL players cannot use this word.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Stat Strip -->
      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-orange-500/30 bg-orange-950/10">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
